title: [The Halfway Midway]
description: Stretching in several directions, several wooden planks are laid upon the ground to provide safe passage through the muck and mire.  Silver ribbons adorned with bells are tied to the low limbs of the surrounding trees, their slightly dented faces glint in the moonlight.
